node.text:
Posted @withregram • @fancyfrancois Another one hits your TV screens this week. 👏🏽 On July 10th THE COUCH airs on @bethertv. All we have to say it get your tissues ready. #stayready #notifications 💚 
#swipe 👉🏽

Mona Scott-Young directs “Almost Enough” which chronicles a day in the life of Patience Williams. Much like her name suggests, Patience has been patiently waiting for her life to become what she’s always wanted. In the meantime, she is rapidly approaching what one could call a mid-mid-life crisis that happened to be exacerbated by Covid-19. All her life, Patience has been that girl  who did everything right. Heavily influenced by her mother and the pressures of being successful, she made all the “right” choices. She was a good student, she went to the right schools, studied the right subjects, got the right degrees, settled in the right city to nail the right job. Yet she’s 10 years post grad, has yet to keep gainful employment, find a real relationship, hit any major life milestones and is experiencing a major downward spiral triggered by depression and anxiety. Can Patience get through this with the help of her new therapist? She is a woman on-the-edge, but of what? Self Healing or Self Harm? 

PREMIERES on JULY 10, 2021 at 10PM on BETher featuring @yandysmith @adwoaduncanwilliams @kellitasmith1 @penwah_penwah and more. 

The “ The Couch “ a BETHer Health Initiative directed by @monascottyoung, Executive produced by @ceoazarel & written by @pattydmac 💚 Stay tuned to watch on @bethertv 🎬

#betherhealthinitiative #mentalhealth #mentalillness #blackfilms #womeninfilmandtv #almostenough #castingdirector #marketingdigital #marketingdirector 

📸: @_just.5_

node.text: I got 6 days to get that flat flat so I hit up my girl @toyajohnson to find out about this Revenge Cleanse I keep hearing about. She told me they have a 3 day and a 7 day cleanse where you can lose 7-25 pounds in 3 or 7 days, respectively. I Said “Sis gimme that 3 day” 😹😹😹😹. I’m taking y’all on this journey because I know so many of y’all want that instant flat flat as well. The key for us is going to be maintaining it. I’m coming back to you for that too @toyajohnson

node.text: Man listen the days and nights with this one used to be insane! We were young fun and ready for the world. I miss those day @annie135. Wether near or far you’ll always be my sister that created some of my best laughs and best memories. Love you long time and HAPPY BIRTHDAY @annie135 😘😘

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Yandy Smith-Harris in Atlanta, Georgia. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: She was proud, her smile infectious, genuine and loyal , a different breed.  All she wanted to do was make a difference in the lives of the people she loved and her community. (Ever thought about What will they say about you in your legacy book?)
